name: Calrissian

Welcome to Calrissian. A collection of useful frameworks and projects for rapid and scalable solutions for big data problems.

For questions and discussions, join our mailing list by sending an email to [calrissian+subscribe@googlegroups.com][calrissian+subscribe@googlegroups.com].
